reviews.title: Defective item
reviews.review_text: I liked the computer, charged it, set it up mostly. Some family crisis came up...went back to finishing the set up. Next time I went to use it, it started flashing on %26 off, so I shut it off to let it rest, tried again, it flashed on and off again. So I decided to let it sit and maybe it will be better after it's totally shut off. In the meantime I looked up to see if I can fix it, people said it took about 5 hours. I thought, it's a brand new computer, I shouldn't have to have it repaired. I don't return things, you can check my record. But this time when I opened it to try it, it was still flashing on and off. I had to return it. So the online robot said I was past the deadline! Well I really tried to make it work and look what I get!!!!!!
